lyrics:
[verse]
I used to think love was what I needed
Chasing hearts, my heart was always bleeding
But now I see, it's time for a change
I'm following my dreams, breaking away from the pain

[chorus]
Chasing dreams, flying high above the sky
No more tears, no more wondering why
Oh, I'm chasing dreams, like I never have before
Leaving it all behind, for the love I can't ignore
